{"tid":2282611,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"CJ ENM秘密會見IZ*ONE各成員所屬社","createTime":"2020-11-12T03:33:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T01:06:22.000Z","uid":1086,"like":21,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"34632b05419ebd8c799079d7a8f33b4fc8f69d47","tid":2282611,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T03:33:17.000Z","msg":"[CJ ENM秘密會見IZ*ONE各成員所屬社，就延長時間的可能性進行討論]11日，據媒體報導，距離IZ*ONE的正式活動還剩下不到半年，在延長合約或結束的十字路 口，內部正在忙碌地進行討論。 據悉，上個月CJ ENM秘密會見了IZ*ONE各成員的所屬社，就延長時間的可能性進行了討論，並探討了今後的活動。 最重要的是成員們的意見，預計新專輯活動結束後將正式展開討論。 就目前而言，組合的回歸活動是優先考慮的問題。<br />\n<br />\n 特別是在因疫情而未能如期舉行巡演或演唱會的情況下，離別對於粉絲們來說也是很遺憾的。 對此，業界出現了&ldquo;IZ*ONE延長說&rdquo;-&ldquo;Unit說&rdquo;等多種說法。 最近，日本首先報導了組合4月活動之後解散的新聞。 在各種傳聞不斷的情況下，CJ ENM方面表示：&ldquo;明年4月解散還沒有決定。 正在討論中。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為IZ*ONE 點起七星燈續命<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></p>"},{"pid":"652ae71b143453e02bb486c6bf45206eb95f6c6e","tid":2282611,"uid":44318,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T03:34:04.000Z","msg":"樓主收皮啦<br />\n扮李露多"},{"pid":"ff86619a8713b7728d2ec831fb2b19ac2751c518","tid":2282611,"uid":374048,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T03:36:16.000Z","msg":"永續IZ*ONE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73312b961371f876c436300fd2d1cefbca14a6c8","tid":2282611,"uid":274876,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T03:41:32.000Z","msg":"永續IZ*ONE 12個缺一不可"},{"pid":"a70816d441d865fd395409e7aa9dcf84e8f95527","tid":2282611,"uid":1984,"like":1,"dislike":1